notesStmt.note: This interview takes place at a reception at an international conference on distributed computing. S1 approaches S8 and S9 and interviews them about their activities in Vienna. They talk about shopping, S8's conference presentation the next day, S1's hometown and S8's job position and the courses he is teaching. There is a very friendly atmosphere and all speakers joke a lot and make ironic and humorous comments.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
